.. table:: Serial Ports Nodes on the System
   :align: center
   :width: 100%
   :widths: auto

   +-----------------------------+-------------------------------+
   | Ports                       | Device Node                   |
   +=============================+===============================+
   | COM1(RS232, Debug)          | /dev/ttyO0                    |
   +-----------------------------+-------------------------------+
   | COM2(RS232)                 | /dev/ttyO1                    |
   +-----------------------------+-------------------------------+
   | COM3(RS485)                 | /dev/ttyO2                    |
   +-----------------------------+-------------------------------+
   | COM4(RS485)                 | /dev/ttyO4                    |
   +-----------------------------+-------------------------------+
